locality: Manongarivo Massif, above village of Ambodisakoana, east of Ankaramy; forested slopes.
Réserve Naturelle Intégrale de Tsaratanana, Beangona, along the crest above the Antsahabe River. Fok. Ambinany Beangona, Fir. Marotolana, Fiv. Ambanja. Plants preserved in alcohol.
Tsaratanana RNI. Hill 1 km south of river Andilambe. Low elevation humid forest (dominated by Uapaca, Garcinia, Canarium and Grungeria).
Between Maivantanana and Antanamarina, next to river Mandrizavona, Ambanja, Antsiranana. Plant collected with C. Birkinshaw and J. Rabenantoandro, preserved in alcohol.
